# CMake — ignore only typical files dropped by an accidental in-source configure at the
# repository root. Out-of-source builds use build/, already ignored above.
# Avoid blanket `*.cmake`: it would untrack real modules (e.g. cmake/*.cmake) if added later.
/CMakeCache.txt
/CMakeFiles/
/cmake_install.cmake
/Makefile

